query: INSERT INTO core_credit_facility_proposal_events (id, recorded_at, sequence, event_type, event, context) SELECT $1, COALESCE($2, NOW()), ROW_NUMBER() OVER () + $3, unnested.event_type, unnested.event, $6 FROM UNNEST($4::text[], $5::jsonb[]) AS unnested(event_type, event) RETURNING recorded_at
